DEFINE
  VAR __DS0Core = 
    FILTER(
      KEEPFILTERS(
        ADDCOLUMNS(
          KEEPFILTERS(VALUES('Date'[Calendar Year])),
          "Sales_Amount", 'Sales'[Sales Amount]
        )
      ),
      NOT(ISBLANK([Sales_Amount]))
    )

  VAR __DS0PrimaryWindowed = 
    TOPN(101, __DS0Core, 'Date'[Calendar Year], 1)

EVALUATE
  __DS0PrimaryWindowed

ORDER BY
  'Date'[Calendar Year]
